## 2026-03-27 - `themedAllTokensFlat` drops tokens outside themed sets
- Added a base layer pass before applying themed sets: collect all set names referenced by any dimension option into `themedSets`, then seed `merged` with every token whose set is NOT in `themedSets`. The existing source→enabled overlay logic then applies on top, so unthemed tokens are always included as a foundation.
